# This repo tracks ONLY the tool and its installer.
# Everything else — dev notes (CLAUDE.md), archived scripts (_archive/), personal
# reference (ssh-config, termux.properties), config, secrets, runtime state — stays
# on disk but is never committed. To also track a new file, add a "!/<name>" line.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/agentbox
!/install.sh
!/templates/

# Secrets & runtime state — never commit, even if the allowlist above is loosened.
# (Last match wins, so these override any "!/..." re-inclusion.)
**/.config/
**/agent.env
**/agent-vpn.conf
**/nothing.conf
**/auth.txt
**/rclone.conf
**/surfshark_configs.zip
**/profiles/
**/bisync/
**/*.pid
**/*.log
.DS_Store
